description: Creates an asset in Amazon DataZone catalog.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: A unique, case-sensitive identifier that is provided to ensure the idempotency of the request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: Amazon DataZone domain where the asset is created.

parameters.description: Metadata forms attached to the asset. (dict) --- The details of a metadata form. content (string) --- The content of the metadata form.
